content: Xander's learning curve is steep but rewarding. Its ability to predict market volatility has improved significantly. Sarah and I had a tech-free day, just exploring the city, reminding ourselves of the world beyond screens.

Launched Xander's new feature for personalized trading strategies. It's a hit with beta users. Also, Sarah and I are planning a trip to the Catskills for some digital detox time. Balancing tech with life's simple pleasures is key.
